            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20six%20branches%20of%20the%20lampstand%20in%20the%20tabernacle%2C%20there%20are%20six%20facets%20of%20the%20Holy%20Spirit's%20character.%20First%2C%20He%20is%20the%20Spirit%20of%20wisdom%2C%20revealing%20to%20us%20His%20future%20purposes%20both%20for%20ourselves%20and%20for%20His%20kingdom.%20Second%2C%20He%20is%20the%20Spirit%20of%20understanding%2C%20giving%20us%20revelation%20about%20our%20present%20situation%20and%20how%20best%20to%20be%20fruitful%20in%20it.%20Third%2C%20He%20is%20the%20Spirit%20of%20counsel%2C%20instructing%20us%20in%20solving%20hard%20problems%20by%20discerning%20the%20root%20causes.%20Fourth%2C%20He%20is%20the%20Spirit%20of%20might%2C%20strengthening%20us%20with%20power%20in%20our%20inner%20man%20and%20anointing%20us%20with%20His%20spiritual%20gifts.%20Fifth%2C%20He%20is%20the%20Spirit%20of%20knowledge%2C%20revealing%20to%20us%20the%20various%20attributes%20of%20Jesus%20in%20the%20Word%20of%20God.%20Finally%2C%20He%20is%20the%20Spirit%20of%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20Lord%2C%20showing%20us%20areas%20of%20our%20lives%20where%20sin%20has%20a%20foothold%20and%20then%20changing%20us%20into%20the%20image%20of%20Christ.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJesus%2C%20the%20%22stump%20of%20David's%20family%22%20(Isaiah%2011%3A1)%2C%20perfectly%20portrayed%20all%20these%20characteristics.%20Ask%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20to%20fill%20you%20today%20with%20these%20six%20attributes%2C%20and%20you%20will%20walk%20like%20Jesus%20walked!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
