            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%2010%3A1-11%3A16%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%20sorrow%20awaits%20the%20unjust%20judges%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20those%20who%20issue%20unfair%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20deprive%20the%20poor%20of%20justice%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20deny%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20needy%20among%20my%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20prey%20on%20widows%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20take%20advantage%20of%20orphans.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%20will%20you%20do%20when%20I%20punish%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhen%20I%20send%20disaster%20upon%20you%20from%20a%20distant%20land%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ETo%20whom%20will%20you%20turn%20for%20help%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWhere%20will%20your%20treasures%20be%20safe%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20stumble%20along%20as%20prisoners%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eor%20lie%20among%20the%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBut%20even%20then%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20anger%20will%20not%20be%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHis%20fist%20is%20still%20poised%20to%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJudgment%20against%20Assyria%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20sorrow%20awaits%20Assyria%2C%20the%20rod%20of%20my%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20use%20it%20as%20a%20club%20to%20express%20my%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20am%20sending%20Assyria%20against%20a%20godless%20nation%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eagainst%20a%20people%20with%20whom%20I%20am%20angry.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EAssyria%20will%20plunder%20them%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Etrampling%20them%20like%20dirt%20beneath%20its%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_7%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria%20will%20not%20understand%20that%20he%20is%20my%20tool%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehis%20mind%20does%20not%20work%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHis%20plan%20is%20simply%20to%20destroy%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20cut%20down%20nation%20after%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_8%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20say%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BEach%20of%20my%20princes%20will%20soon%20be%20a%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_9%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20destroyed%20Calno%20just%20as%20we%20did%20Carchemish.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHamath%20fell%20before%20us%20as%20Arpad%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAnd%20we%20destroyed%20Samaria%20just%20as%20we%20did%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_10%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EYes%2C%20we%20have%20finished%20off%20many%20a%20kingdom%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhose%20gods%20were%20greater%20than%20those%20in%20Jerusalem%20and%20Samaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_11%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20we%20will%20defeat%20Jerusalem%20and%20her%20gods%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ejust%20as%20we%20destroyed%20Samaria%20with%20hers.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_12%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20the%20Lord%20has%20used%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria%20to%20accomplish%20his%20purposes%20on%20Mount%20Zion%20and%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20he%20will%20turn%20against%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria%20and%20punish%20him%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20he%20is%20proud%20and%20arrogant.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_10_13%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20boasts%2C%20%3C%2Fv